---
layout: page
title: Writing
---
<p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-8 -mt-4">
  On software, life in Germany, and whatever else catches my attention.
  <a href="{{ "/posts/archive" | relative_url }}" class="underline underline-offset-2 decoration-slate-300 hover:decoration-slate-900 transition-colors">Browse the archive</a>.
</p>

<div class="flex flex-col">
  {% for post in collections.posts.resources %}
  <a href="{{ post.relative_url }}" class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-6 py-3 border-b border-slate-100 last:border-0 group no-underline" style="text-decoration:none">
    <span class="text-sm text-slate-800 group-hover:text-slate-500 transition-colors duration-150">{{ post.title }}</span>
    <time class="text-xs text-slate-400 shrink-0">{{ post.data.date | date: '%b %d, %Y' }}</time>
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
